query:
SELECT 
  '12@supplier.com supplier ID' as info,
  su.supplierId as value
FROM users u 
JOIN supplierUsers su ON u.id = su.userId 
WHERE u.email = '12@supplier.com'

UNION ALL

SELECT 
  CONCAT('Job ', id, ' assigned to supplier') as info,
  assignedSupplierId as value
FROM jobs 
WHERE id IN (30001, 90001)
ORDER BY info
